pageProduct.name: Aussie Bodies Protein Bar Lo Carb Crunchy Rocky Road 40g
pageProduct.description:
General Information

12g PROTEIN
2.0g SUGARS
HIGH FIBRE
No artificial colours or preservatives

Our Pro-active Nutrition products help your shape body from the inside out. Since 1991

Product Claims: With, MILK CHOCOLATE, MARSHMALLOWS, PEANUTS, CHIA SEEDS, 12g PROTEIN , 2.0g SUGARS , HIGH FIBRE, No artificial colours or preservatives

Size: 40g

Flavour: Rocky Road Crunch

Serving Size: 40g

Servings Per Pack: 1

KEY FEATURES

• Proactive Nutrition
• Great Tasting
• Guilt-Free Indulgence
• Source of Protein

Ingredients

INGREDIENTS: Aussie Bodies® Protein Blend (36%) (Soy Protein Crisps (Soy Protein Isolate, Cocoa Powder, Tapioca Starch, Salt), Whey Protein Concentrate (Milk), Milk Protein Concentrate), No Added Sugar Milk Chocolate (25%) (Sweeteners (Polydextrose, Erythritol, Monk Fruit Extract, Steviol Glycosides), Cocoa Butter, Milk Solids, Cocoa Mass, Inulin, Emulsifier (Soy Lecithin), Flavour), Sweeteners [Polydextrose, Maltitol (Wheat)], Peanuts (3%), Humectant (Glycerol), Vegetable Fat, Butter (Milk), Marshmallows (1.5%) [Natural Colour (Carmines)], Vegetable Gums (Acacia Gum, Xanthan Gum), Black Chia Seeds (1%), Flavour, Salt, Emulsifier (Soy Lecithin).

Contains: Contains: Milk, Soy, Cereals Contain Gluten (Wheat) and Peanuts.
May Contain: Cereals Contain Gluten (Oats) Tree Nuts (Almonds, Hazelnuts) and Sesame Seeds.

Allergen Contains: Milk| Peanuts| Soy| Wheat| Cereals Containing Gluten

Allergen May Be Present: Almonds| Hazelnuts| Oats| Sesame Seeds| Tree Nuts| Cereals Containing Gluten

Directions

Store in a cool, dry place, below 30°C. Keep out of direct sunlight.
